  "description": "A mod that just adds some simple hookshots to the game.",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"215\" height=\"72\" title=\"Fabric API\" alt=\"Fabric API\"></a>\n\n---\n\nHookshot is a small mod that adds a grappling hook-like tool for the player to use to get around.\n\nHookshot:\n- Default range of 24 blocks\n- Aquatic Modifier lets the hookshot glide through water\n- Enderic Modifier teleports instead of pulls\n- Quick Modifier speeds up the reeling by 50%\n- Long Modifier doubles the range\n- Automatic modifier automatically diconnects the hook\n\n---\n\n<table align=\"center\">\n    <tr>\n        <th><b>Join my Discord</b></th>\n        <th><b>Join my Ko-Fi!</b></th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <th><a href=\"https://discord.gg/f5dFYWX\"><img src=\"https://cammiescorner.dev/images/extras/discord.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" title=\"Cammie's Corner Discord\" alt=\"Cammie's Corner Discord\"></a></th>\n        <th><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/camellias/tiers\"><img src=\"https://cammiescorner.dev/images/extras/kofi.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" title=\"Cammie's Corner Patreon\" alt=\"Cammie's Corner Patreon\"></a></th>\n    </tr>\n</table>",
